00:38:43.880 --> 00:38:44.559
Iginiit ng taong ito...

00:38:47.599 --> 00:38:49.119
Sige, pwede ka nang lumabas muna.

00:38:53.280 --> 00:38:55.119
Bakit ka dumating nang hindi man lang nagpapaalam?

00:38:55.679 --> 00:38:56.880
Ang dami kong gagawin ngayon.

00:38:56.880 --> 00:38:57.880
Kailangan mo akong hintayin.

00:38:58.079 --> 00:38:59.159
Busy ka, busy ka.

00:39:09.400 --> 00:39:11.320
Sige, puwede tayong maging masaya pag-uwi.

00:39:12.559 --> 00:39:14.079
Masyado akong abala ngayon.

00:39:15.079 --> 00:39:16.719
Maaari mo sana akong bigyan ng paunang abiso.

00:39:17.079 --> 00:39:18.000
Namiss kita.

00:39:18.000 --> 00:39:18.920
Namiss din kita.

00:39:19.239 --> 00:39:20.360
Talaga?

00:39:20.679 --> 00:39:21.920
Nagmamasid ang mga tao.

00:39:23.920 --> 00:39:25.559
Ako ay...

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:28.880
Medyo naging busy talaga ako nitong mga nakaraang araw.

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:30.760
Pasensya na, nahuli ako.

00:39:30.920 --> 00:39:32.599
Tungkol sa bagay na ito kay Peng Le Xuan,

00:39:32.599 --> 00:39:33.920
Kuya, Pangalawang Kuya, Weiguo...

00:39:33.920 --> 00:39:35.239
magkayakap sila.

00:39:35.239 --> 00:39:36.760
Mahal, may tawag ako.

00:39:36.760 --> 00:39:37.679
Hintayin mo ako sandali, ha?

00:39:40.760 --> 00:39:43.000
Pangulong Huang, nakita ko na ang kontrata.

00:39:45.159 --> 00:39:48.039
Medyo iba ito sa napag-usapan natin.

00:39:49.519 --> 00:39:50.599
Sandali lang.

00:39:54.800 --> 00:39:56.400
Hindi pa ito narerebisa sa kontrata.

00:39:56.639 --> 00:39:57.280
Tama.

00:39:59.480 --> 00:40:02.119
At saka, nariyan din ang promotional content.

00:40:04.159 --> 00:40:05.480
Ang pangunahing bagay ay...

00:40:07.920 --> 00:40:08.880
Oo, oo.

00:40:09.159 --> 00:40:10.800
Sa ngayon, wala pang malinaw na...

00:40:10.800 --> 00:40:13.719
Tungkol ito sa aming naka-iskedyul na livestream na may temang iyon.

00:40:17.079 --> 00:40:17.920
Sa ganoong kaso...

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:19.440
Sige, paalam.

00:40:21.679 --> 00:40:24.119
Marami talaga akong gagawin ngayon.

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:33.039
Pulot

00:40:37.039 --> 00:40:40.239
Hindi ba't nangako ako na bibilhan kita ng bag dati?

00:40:42.159 --> 00:40:43.119
Tingnan mo.

00:40:44.480 --> 00:40:45.159
Tingnan mo.

00:40:47.960 --> 00:40:49.400
Sandali lang, sandali lang.

00:40:49.400 --> 00:40:50.079
Sandali lang.

00:40:50.960 --> 00:40:53.239
Mahal, dapat bawasan mo ang ganitong gastusin sa hinaharap.

00:40:53.840 --> 00:40:56.239
Hindi, itong bag lang talaga...

00:40:56.239 --> 00:40:57.400
Nangako ako.

00:40:57.400 --> 00:40:58.039
Iniisip ko...

00:40:58.039 --> 00:41:00.039
Kung may pera tayo, dapat muna natin itong itabi.

00:41:01.199 --> 00:41:01.880
Ah, tama.

00:41:02.039 --> 00:41:03.880
Ang taas ng performance bonus ko ngayong buwan.

00:41:04.000 --> 00:41:05.559
Mga limampung libo iyon.

00:41:05.679 --> 00:41:06.440
Ilagay natin ito sa ipon.

00:41:06.440 --> 00:41:07.599
Huwag mo munang hawakan 'yan ngayon, ha?

00:41:07.599 --> 00:41:08.320
Magkano?

00:41:08.320 --> 00:41:08.960
Limampung libo.

00:41:13.880 --> 00:41:15.960
Halos tatlong buwan na iyon ng sweldo ko.

00:41:16.719 --> 00:41:17.719
Kahit gaano pa ako kahirap magtrabaho...

00:41:17.719 --> 00:41:19.280
...hindi nito kayang sabayan ang ginagastos mo.

00:41:19.280 --> 00:41:20.320
Tingnan mo itong biyahe mo.

00:41:20.320 --> 00:41:21.760
Isang bag, mga bulaklak...

00:41:21.760 --> 00:41:23.000
Parang wala kang pakialam sa gastos.

00:41:23.239 --> 00:41:24.199
Hindi, hindi.

00:41:24.199 --> 00:41:25.960
Last-minute deal lang ang ticket, napakamura.

00:41:26.159 --> 00:41:26.920
Tungkol naman sa bag na ito...

00:41:26.920 --> 00:41:28.719
Teka, may meeting pa ako.

00:41:29.039 --> 00:41:30.760
Mag-uusap pa tayo pagbalik ko, ha?

00:41:30.880 --> 00:41:32.159
Kailan ito matatapos?

00:41:32.159 --> 00:41:33.119
Hindi ko alam.

00:41:33.559 --> 00:41:34.440
Kailan ka babalik?

00:41:34.440 --> 00:41:35.440
Mahirap sabihin.

00:41:36.440 --> 00:41:38.159
Hindi mo alam, at mahirap sabihin.

00:41:39.000 --> 00:41:40.320
Puro mga tandang pananong ang lahat.

00:41:42.119 --> 00:41:43.440
Kung gayon, ano ang dapat kong gawin?

